&lt;li&gt;Instrument test runs with profiling and APM tooling to identify throughput bottlenecks and latency regressions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build scalable performance test harnesses using Locust, k6, or equivalent frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaboration &amp;amp; Communication:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a technical lead and quality champion, influencing engineering culture, coding standards, and test coverage expectations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor mid-level and senior engineers on automation patterns, code quality, and testing strategy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with product managers to define acceptance criteria and quality gates at the story level&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive root cause analysis on escaped defects and build preventive test coverage&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
